data.prompt:
The IVR has requested the NPI number. Read the 10-digit NPI clearly, one digit at a time with a brief pause between each:

State or enter the NPI:  wwww{{provider_npi}}

After providing the NPI, wait for the IVR to confirm or provide the next prompt.

The IVR has requested the Tax ID number. Read the 9-digit TIN clearly, one digit at a time with a brief pause between each:

TIN: {{provider_tin}}

After providing the TIN, wait for the IVR to confirm or provide the next prompt.
